WEBVTT

00:00.174 --> 00:05.122
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

00:06.094 --> 00:08.802
♪ My heart is racing ♪

00:09.934 --> 00:13.942
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

00:13.966 --> 00:18.722
♪ Hey, when I imagine you ♪

00:19.758 --> 00:22.786
♪ What kind of look ♪

00:23.790 --> 00:27.734
♪ Attracted me to you ♪

00:27.758 --> 00:31.030
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:31.054 --> 00:34.518
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:34.542 --> 00:39.790
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:39.790 --> 00:41.408
♪ I love you ♪

00:41.408 --> 00:44.886
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:44.910 --> 00:48.182
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:48.206 --> 00:53.878
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:53.902 --> 00:55.246
♪ I love you ♪

00:55.246 --> 00:58.582
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:58.606 --> 01:01.954
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:02.062 --> 01:07.259
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:07.259 --> 01:08.942
♪ I love you ♪

01:08.942 --> 01:12.342
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

01:12.366 --> 01:15.766
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:15.790 --> 01:21.366
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:21.390 --> 01:24.802
♪ I love you ♪

01:27.080 --> 01:27.870
=Love Me, Love My Voice=

01:27.870 --> 01:31.122
=Love Me, Love My Voice=
=Episode 30=

01:31.774 --> 01:34.194
(Would you like some soda?)

01:34.977 --> 01:39.637
Mo Qingcheng is all over his wife
and ignores her classmate.

01:47.456 --> 01:51.516
- Is it a bad time?
- You are late to catch on.

01:51.736 --> 01:56.596
- Shall we leave?
- And make her throw away the smoothies?

02:04.336 --> 02:05.956
Let me help her.

02:08.456 --> 02:10.236
What should we do?

02:10.977 --> 02:12.236
I...

02:17.176 --> 02:19.877
- Should we give them a push?
- How?

02:20.217 --> 02:23.197
Set up an image for Zhou.

02:24.296 --> 02:25.477
Watch this.

02:33.896 --> 02:36.833
- That's my seat.
- Let me take a few bites.

02:36.857 --> 02:39.597
Aren't you very generous?

02:39.776 --> 02:41.437
Yeah. Go ahead.

02:42.217 --> 02:43.552
Both mango-flavored.

02:43.576 --> 02:45.357
- Thanks.
- Thanks.

02:57.176 --> 02:59.076
It's freezing. Slow down.

02:59.736 --> 03:02.676
See? And he's considerate.

03:04.537 --> 03:08.956
Zhou, I heard that you had a hard time
starting the business.

03:09.657 --> 03:12.466
- Why?
- Just chitchatting.

03:12.736 --> 03:15.673
We're trying to learn
from your glorious past.

03:15.697 --> 03:20.956
- Starting a business is always hard.
- Tell us more about it.

03:28.336 --> 03:33.113
We had to get business
and go to the hospitals all day.

03:33.137 --> 03:36.513
Yeah, it was very tiring
at the beginning.

03:36.537 --> 03:41.953
He couldn't eat and could barely
sleep for a few hours every day, right?

03:41.977 --> 03:47.272
In the end, his girlfriend broke up
with him, and he remained single.

03:47.296 --> 03:50.633
He is such a nice guy.

03:50.657 --> 03:54.757
How come he's still single, right?

04:03.937 --> 04:09.032
Mo Bai, if you have nothing to do,
eat some more, okay?

04:09.056 --> 04:10.953
Keep your mouth shut.

04:10.977 --> 04:14.436
Why are you getting shy?
Fine, I'll be quiet.

04:15.136 --> 04:19.912
- Didn't you want to see the lighthouse?
- What about my smoothie?

04:19.936 --> 04:21.717
- Take it with you.
- You...

04:22.777 --> 04:26.277
He's got a temper.
I'll leave you to talk.

04:27.457 --> 04:30.996
- I'm still building up the vibe.
- That's enough.

04:34.017 --> 04:36.236
Don't listen to them.

05:05.217 --> 05:07.116
Have it. Don't catch a cold.

05:07.696 --> 05:11.277
- Aren't you cold?
- No, I'm well-built.

05:13.176 --> 05:15.556
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

05:30.736 --> 05:32.957
It's already 2:00. Let me walk you back.

05:38.136 --> 05:39.236
Okay.

05:40.736 --> 05:42.996
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

05:44.256 --> 05:48.196
I'll walk you back and then walk around.

05:48.777 --> 05:50.357
Aren't you sleepy?

05:51.977 --> 05:54.477
I forgot to tell you.

05:55.017 --> 05:56.717
Mr. Mo

05:57.256 --> 06:00.190
sent me a message that
Sheng fell asleep in my room

06:00.190 --> 06:02.792
and told me to sleep out.

06:02.816 --> 06:06.553
I guess I'd rather take a walk out here

06:06.577 --> 06:09.176
than sleep on the rattan chair.

06:09.176 --> 06:11.556
You can't walk all night.

06:18.256 --> 06:19.636
Then...

06:21.777 --> 06:24.517
- How about...
- No.

06:24.657 --> 06:28.116
I'm not trying to sleep in your room.

06:28.417 --> 06:30.357
Don't get me wrong.

06:32.577 --> 06:35.357
I'm not sleepy yet. I can walk with you.

06:38.897 --> 06:42.534
It's a long shore.

06:42.558 --> 06:46.316
Maybe we can walk until dawn
and see the sunrise.

06:48.936 --> 06:52.756
You're getting slower. Are you tired?

06:54.657 --> 06:57.816
Maybe it's because of the ascending.
I am a bit tired.

06:57.816 --> 07:01.077
Let's sit here for a break.

07:01.616 --> 07:02.756
Okay.

07:11.777 --> 07:14.357
Actually, I enjoy talking to you.

07:16.056 --> 07:19.397
Me too.

07:24.376 --> 07:26.796
So let's talk more.

07:28.736 --> 07:30.636
Sure. About what?

07:32.136 --> 07:34.277
About how you started the business.

07:35.056 --> 07:38.157
How I started the business.

07:40.296 --> 07:43.056
Well, when I was a kid,

07:43.056 --> 07:46.553
I was a troublemaker
and never studied, you know?

07:46.577 --> 07:52.577
Then I met Mo Qingcheng
and Feng Yasong after I graduated.

07:52.577 --> 07:56.796
I thought I shouldn't be left behind.

07:56.857 --> 08:00.157
So I worked hard to start the business.

08:00.977 --> 08:04.477
Come to think of it,
it's important to have good friends.

08:04.577 --> 08:08.876
A good influence keeps you motivated.

08:08.936 --> 08:12.597
- Yeah, that's me and Sheng.
- Right?

08:13.457 --> 08:19.876
Thanks to my buddies, I started
my business relatively smoothly.

08:20.337 --> 08:22.677
I guess I made it.

08:40.016 --> 08:45.036
So how did you
break up with your girlfriend?

08:53.736 --> 08:59.276
It was tiring to start the business
and I didn't have time for her.

08:59.337 --> 09:03.116
We slowly lost passion and broke up.

09:03.857 --> 09:05.197
Peacefully.

09:08.736 --> 09:10.236
Who brought it up?

09:11.857 --> 09:12.996
She did.

09:16.016 --> 09:19.077
Didn't you try to get her back?

09:20.937 --> 09:24.717
No, I think love has to be mutual.

09:25.457 --> 09:28.690
It takes two people
to have a relationship, after all.

09:29.214 --> 09:34.437
One-sided love doesn't lead anywhere.

09:36.376 --> 09:41.036
I agree that love should be mutual.

09:44.697 --> 09:46.636
Everybody needs feedback.

10:06.496 --> 10:08.477
Well, that's it.

10:08.736 --> 10:11.797
Let's keep walking.
It's getting cold sitting here, right?

10:12.217 --> 10:13.717
- Let's go then.
- Alright.

10:13.977 --> 10:15.197
Let's go.

10:17.616 --> 10:22.116
Let's talk about you. Any plans?

10:23.016 --> 10:27.797
I want to get my postgraduate degree
and find a job I like.

10:28.217 --> 10:32.357
Hopefully, I can find someone I like
who also likes me.

11:20.857 --> 11:23.317
I actually slept here the whole night.

11:29.016 --> 11:30.516
Where is Xiaoxing?

11:46.736 --> 11:49.077
I deserve a massage, okay?

11:50.416 --> 11:51.416
Morning.

11:52.656 --> 11:55.357
I'll go upstairs to wash up.

12:05.937 --> 12:08.677
You're finally back.

12:12.656 --> 12:14.717
Juemei slept here last night?

12:15.582 --> 12:17.170
Of course not.

12:17.534 --> 12:21.913
You ditched me for your boyfriend.
I stayed up all night. I'm so sleepy.

12:21.937 --> 12:23.996
You stayed up all night?

12:24.857 --> 12:26.957
Not only that,

12:27.697 --> 12:29.717
we went

12:31.016 --> 12:35.036
for a walk until dawn.

12:35.776 --> 12:37.592
I was about to head back,

12:37.616 --> 12:41.033
but Mr. Mo texted Juemei that

12:41.057 --> 12:44.632
his wife had fallen asleep
and that he should sleep out.

12:44.656 --> 12:49.872
Where could he go?
So I walked with him all night.

12:49.896 --> 12:57.077
I can't invite him over for the night.
I have to be discreet.

13:01.896 --> 13:04.597
My legs are sore. Massage them.

13:05.937 --> 13:10.597
So Juemei was very decent
and didn't ask to share your bed.

13:12.057 --> 13:15.677
H-He is very decent.

13:17.697 --> 13:19.477
It's only 6:00. Let me sleep more.

13:24.977 --> 13:27.717
Tell me what you did.

13:29.097 --> 13:31.913
Nothing. I was sleepy.

13:31.937 --> 13:35.557
You took a nap in the afternoon
but I only slept for ten minutes.

13:36.736 --> 13:38.578
So I fell asleep.

13:39.136 --> 13:40.357
That's it?

13:42.857 --> 13:45.717
Gu Sheng, you're so insensitive.

13:47.016 --> 13:48.197
Sleep.

13:54.337 --> 13:58.957
You should massage my legs, okay?
I walked the whole night.

14:00.016 --> 14:01.797
Don't you want to say something?

14:04.016 --> 14:07.636
Stop smiling. What a surprise.

14:08.177 --> 14:10.557
You favor your girlfriend
over your buddies.

14:13.857 --> 14:18.276
Think about it from another aspect.
I was creating opportunities for you.

14:18.846 --> 14:22.116
Creating opportunities? What for?

14:29.776 --> 14:34.636
- You think too much, okay?
- Yeah?

14:39.457 --> 14:44.876
But even if I'm interested,
I can't just sleep over at her place.

14:46.937 --> 14:50.516
Don't you know that we're just friends?

14:51.337 --> 14:52.636
I knew it.

14:53.256 --> 14:55.236
You're a decent guy.

14:56.536 --> 15:02.156
But you talked the whole night. You must
have learned more about each other.

15:11.057 --> 15:16.957
Mo Qingcheng, you're playing
tricks on me, huh? Just wait.

15:18.616 --> 15:19.616
Just wait.

15:21.857 --> 15:23.837
You have to be grateful.

15:31.102 --> 15:32.536
(Intercontinental
One Thousand Island Lake Resort)

15:32.536 --> 15:33.553
Sir, this way.

15:33.577 --> 15:35.352
- Come on, sir, this way.
- Enough.

15:35.376 --> 15:36.702
- Come on.
- Feishao.

15:36.702 --> 15:39.717
Food is ready. Grab a seat.

15:40.937 --> 15:43.276
- Grab a seat.
- So many dishes.

15:43.736 --> 15:45.717
Send a photo to Zhu.

15:46.656 --> 15:48.937
- Sit in front of me.
- Thanks.

15:48.937 --> 15:51.597
- Sit here.
- I'll be next to Doudou.

15:52.057 --> 15:53.156
Xiaoxing.

15:53.857 --> 15:55.697
- Where do I sit?
- Sit anywhere you want.

15:55.697 --> 15:56.697
- Really?
- Sit here.

15:56.697 --> 15:59.712
- Come here.
- Zheng, I want to sit next to you.

15:59.736 --> 16:03.632
Guys, they make great fish here.

16:03.656 --> 16:06.472
It's still midday. Let's dig in.

16:06.496 --> 16:09.553
- Then let's drive the off-roader, okay?
- Alright.

16:09.577 --> 16:11.232
- Here.
- This is tender.

16:11.256 --> 16:12.992
- What's this?
- Tofu.

16:13.016 --> 16:16.156
- Where is the fish?
- Have some fish.

16:17.136 --> 16:19.276
- It's good.
- Is it?

16:19.937 --> 16:21.396
Thank you.

16:21.736 --> 16:24.156
- It's so nice.
- Dig in.

16:29.016 --> 16:32.437
Doudou, can you
put an extra bed in your room?

16:33.817 --> 16:35.636
- Yeah, why?
- Thanks.

16:35.736 --> 16:39.597
Let Xiaoxing share your room.
It's livelier like this.

16:40.297 --> 16:42.156
What about Sheng?

16:44.097 --> 16:48.317
She's scared of the dark.
How is she going to sleep alone?

16:49.736 --> 16:52.273
Yeah, they are fine together.

16:52.297 --> 16:54.716
Why would she squeeze at my place?

16:57.936 --> 17:02.057
Doudou, here. Have some fish heads.
It's good for the brain.

17:02.057 --> 17:07.436
Are you so close to Xiaoxing now?
You're arranging for her accommodation?

17:14.176 --> 17:17.152
- Cousin, want some fish soup?
- Yeah, thanks.

17:17.176 --> 17:18.317
You're welcome.

17:24.656 --> 17:32.237
- Isn't he taking good care of her?
- H-He's fine. There's a long way to go.

17:33.696 --> 17:34.956
Have a shrimp.

17:36.936 --> 17:38.313
What's going on?

17:38.337 --> 17:40.993
- Are you eating it or not?
- Yeah.

17:41.017 --> 17:44.037
You got it for me.
Of course, I'd eat it.

17:47.777 --> 17:50.116
It's nice. Try it.

17:52.057 --> 17:53.396
Have some meat.

17:59.057 --> 18:01.997
- Slowly. Be careful of the bones.
- Let me teach you.

18:02.777 --> 18:03.997
Teach me.

18:04.976 --> 18:07.037
Why's the watermelon so sweet?

18:07.817 --> 18:13.392
- Mr. Mu, have a pineapple. Be sour.
- Let me peel a shrimp for you.

18:13.416 --> 18:17.513
Come on, you didn't remove the shell
or clean the sand vein.

18:17.537 --> 18:20.553
Loners help loners. Sure.
Peel one for me. I'll eat it.

18:20.577 --> 18:22.557
- Alright, wait.
- Seriously.

18:25.136 --> 18:27.912
- I'm a VIP. I know everything.
- Alright.

18:27.936 --> 18:30.357
- Take this one.
- I'll ask you for help.

18:31.857 --> 18:38.057
Guys, this is off-roader driving,
the most special event here.

18:38.057 --> 18:41.837
- Nice cars.
- Why is it the most special?

18:42.216 --> 18:46.632
The route is complicated.
It's very thrilling. Take a look.

18:46.656 --> 18:51.872
The mountain road
is narrow, bumpy, and lengthy.

18:51.896 --> 18:55.833
- It's one of a kind.
- Not bad.

18:55.857 --> 18:57.833
You make it sound like
we're here to suffer.

18:57.857 --> 19:00.033
Aren't we here to enjoy the excitement?

19:00.057 --> 19:04.592
Let's form groups of two.
Couples should share a car.

19:04.616 --> 19:07.797
It's a perfect chance
to get closer to each other.

19:08.456 --> 19:13.557
There's only one couple.
The others can team up as they want.

19:16.337 --> 19:19.716
- Only one couple.
- Enough.

19:21.857 --> 19:25.592
I prepared handkerchiefs for you.
It's going to be very dusty.

19:25.616 --> 19:28.753
And it's a long way. Cover your face.

19:28.777 --> 19:33.192
- Lady first. One for each. Xiaoxing.
- You're very considerate today.

19:33.216 --> 19:35.716
- He became so thoughtful.
- Caring.

19:35.857 --> 19:37.192
- The nice guy.
- I want this one.

19:37.216 --> 19:38.872
- Come on, Sheng.
- This one.

19:38.896 --> 19:42.033
- Come on, pick one.
- Guys, pick yours.

19:42.057 --> 19:44.033
I'll show you how to wear it.

19:44.057 --> 19:46.416
Mine is too colorful. Let's exchange.

19:46.416 --> 19:49.837
- You know how to do it? Amazing.
- Let me help.

19:50.497 --> 19:52.956
- Here.
- Help Xiaoxing.

19:55.097 --> 19:57.916
- Give it to me, honey.
- Thanks, Doudou.

19:58.456 --> 20:03.476
It's going to be dusty on the road.
Just leave your eyes out.

20:05.656 --> 20:07.797
- Is it too tight?
- It's alright.

20:08.976 --> 20:11.352
- Loners help loners.
- Sure.

20:11.376 --> 20:12.753
- Help me.
- Let me.

20:12.777 --> 20:14.896
- Come on.
- Come on, Feishao. Let me help.

20:14.896 --> 20:15.896
Come on.

20:17.456 --> 20:18.757
Tell me if it's tight.

20:20.297 --> 20:21.317
Is it tight?

20:22.936 --> 20:25.156
- Alright.
- Alright.

20:27.257 --> 20:29.237
- Get in the car.
- Thanks, Doudou.

20:30.337 --> 20:31.357
Pick a car.

20:31.936 --> 20:33.513
- That one.
- Okay.

20:33.537 --> 20:34.837
Let's go.

20:35.616 --> 20:38.432
- What are you doing?
- So rare. You're not following her.

20:38.456 --> 20:42.476
- Do you have to be so sarcastic?
- It depends on my mood.

20:43.577 --> 20:45.793
I feel sorry for you.
Let's share the ride.

20:45.817 --> 20:49.553
- Don't.
- You're the only outsider here.

20:49.577 --> 20:52.592
- I'll register an account tomorrow.
- Then I'll be your senior.

20:52.616 --> 20:55.476
- Whatever.
- Pick a car.

20:56.017 --> 20:58.997
- Well...
- Someone's calling you. Go.

21:01.337 --> 21:03.757
- Be careful.
- Okay.

21:05.857 --> 21:10.152
- So, let's share one.
- Alright, agreed.

21:10.176 --> 21:12.297
- We all go in couples.
- I agree too.

21:12.297 --> 21:15.997
- Just share a car.
- Mind your own business.

21:16.497 --> 21:20.997
Mu, that one matches
our clothes. Let's go get it.

21:22.257 --> 21:23.192
We...

21:23.216 --> 21:26.233
- Doudou, what's going on?
- See? Keep your mouth shut.

21:26.257 --> 21:27.616
- Fasten the seat belt.
- And this one.

21:27.616 --> 21:29.473
You too.

21:29.497 --> 21:31.317
Don't play dirty.

21:31.456 --> 21:33.116
- Let me.
- First come, first served.

21:33.337 --> 21:35.577
- I got it first.
- Don't play dirty.

21:35.577 --> 21:38.357
- Wait for the next time.
- Seriously.

21:49.497 --> 21:51.116
Wait, slow down.

21:52.537 --> 21:53.997
Safety first.

21:55.777 --> 21:57.716
Fasten it.

22:01.216 --> 22:03.112
- Thanks.
- Thank you, Mr. Mo.

22:03.136 --> 22:04.597
See you.

22:05.257 --> 22:07.872
- Won't you check on me?
- So considerate.

22:07.896 --> 22:11.912
He's not only nice to Sheng.
He's nice to everyone. Perfect.

22:11.936 --> 22:14.916
Let's observe more.

22:17.777 --> 22:20.476
Mr. Mo, done with fan service?

22:21.416 --> 22:22.916
Is he just a fan?

22:24.017 --> 22:26.876
Kill two birds with one rock.
Impressive, Mr. Mo.

22:31.456 --> 22:35.872
I come here every month.
So follow me and stay safe, okay?

22:35.896 --> 22:39.196
- Okay.
- Slowly. Be careful.

23:14.616 --> 23:16.116
You got this?

23:16.777 --> 23:21.517
- Mu, can't you go faster?
- Safety comes first.

23:57.656 --> 23:59.517
Catch up with them.

24:18.857 --> 24:22.636
- Here we go.
- Is it ready?

24:23.616 --> 24:24.833
- This one is ready.
- Okay.

24:24.857 --> 24:26.136
- Here.
- Okay.

24:26.136 --> 24:28.196
- Bring me a plate. It's ready.
- Here.

24:32.017 --> 24:34.576
- Have a skewer.
- Thanks, Doudou.

24:34.576 --> 24:36.156
- No problem.
- What's this?

24:37.017 --> 24:39.192
- Mr. Mo grilled it. Have it.
- Thanks.

24:39.216 --> 24:40.632
- Stop taking photos.
- Pork belly.

24:40.656 --> 24:42.396
- Here.
- It's amazing. Try it.

24:43.097 --> 24:45.077
- Pork belly.
- Here.

24:45.376 --> 24:46.257
- Try it.
- So many.

24:46.257 --> 24:48.277
- Smells nice.
- Add some pepper.

24:50.057 --> 24:50.952
It's burning.

24:50.976 --> 24:53.597
- It's ready.
- Okay, thanks.

24:54.857 --> 24:59.793
Barbecue by the lake. Food and view.
But something is missing.

24:59.817 --> 25:01.112
What can it be?

25:01.136 --> 25:06.416
Nice view. Nice cuisine.
Shouldn't we ask Mr. Mo to sing for us?

25:06.416 --> 25:07.912
- Yeah.
- Right?

25:07.936 --> 25:09.592
Yeah.

25:09.616 --> 25:10.716
Alright.

25:11.696 --> 25:14.896
- Really?
- You're not interested?

25:14.896 --> 25:18.517
I'm just surprised. What would you sing?

25:20.176 --> 25:21.237
Dawn and Dusk.

25:21.896 --> 25:27.156
Dawn and Dusk.
Isn't that someone's love song?

25:27.537 --> 25:32.837
- It's lonely to sing it alone.
- It has to be sung by a couple.

25:33.696 --> 25:37.073
- Shall we?
- Of course, I'll join you.

25:37.097 --> 25:39.156
Then I'll be the accompaniment.

25:40.017 --> 25:43.192
- Sheng, which key do you want?
- A-flat.

25:43.216 --> 25:45.513
A-flat.

25:45.537 --> 25:46.817
- Let me.
- You're next.

