34:50.942 --> 34:53.254
I'm glad it worked. Stop laughing.

34:53.313 --> 34:56.370
- It's always tough at the beginning. Try again.
- Okay.

34:56.913 --> 34:58.853
Relax your shoulders.

34:59.473 --> 35:00.794
