- Let go.

35:07.390 --> 35:08.813
Alright, one more.

35:10.313 --> 35:11.374
Let's go.

35:12.465 --> 35:15.005
I'm tired.
I can't pull the string anymore.

35:22.266 --> 35:27.485
Align your eye, arrow tip,
and bull's eye.

35:28.666 --> 35:31.766
Let go fast. One, two, three.

35:35.866 --> 35:39.886
- You're amazing.
- You're amazing. Fast learner.

35:40.826 --> 35:42.886
- One more.
- Okay.

35:44.030 --> 35:49.822
Put the hand here. Otherwise, you don't
have the power to pull the string.

35:49.822 --> 35:53.485
Hold it here.
Yeah, put it under your jaw.

35:53.585 --> 35:57.726
