Three shots. Whoever scores higher wins.

36:44.382 --> 36:47.886
Track No.1. Track No.2.
Start with Track No.1.

36:49.425 --> 36:50.202
Go for it.

36:50.226 --> 36:53.081
Let him win, okay? Don't steal his show.

36:53.105 --> 36:55.525
No way. I have to teach him a lesson.

36:57.505 --> 36:59.206
I'll let him win
by one point for each shot.

37:06.666 --> 37:10.286
