38:17.545 --> 38:19.666
Will you make it?

38:23.186 --> 38:27.521
Wang Ke, sixth ring. It's a draw.

38:27.545 --> 38:31.925
- I told you the fifth ring.
- It flew up a bit, okay?

38:35.985 --> 38:37.246
Seventh ring.

38:47.866 --> 38:51.766
- Eighth ring.
- Zhou Zheng, eighth ring.

38:51.945 --> 38:53.346
Impressive, Mr. Zhou.

38:53.346 --> 38:58.162
This is the final shot.
Wang Ke is under huge pressure.

38:58.186 --> 39:00.686
Stop it. I'm so nervous.

39:02.826 --> 39:07.726
Let's see how he does in the final shot.

39:13.306 --> 39:16.826
Wang Ke, seventh ring.
I hereby announce the result.

39:16.826 --> 39:21.286
The winner is Zhou Zheng with 21 points.

39:24.226 --> 39:26.706
- Zheng, you're amazing.
- Careful.

39:26.706 --> 39:32.065
Way to go, Juemei. You defeated
