39:32.065 --> 39:35.441
- Semi-professional? You're an amateur.
- Too easy.

39:35.465 --> 39:38.005
You were even stepping on the line.

39:38.226 --> 39:42.726
- You're right, Mr. Zhou.
- Three, two, one. Let go.

39:48.105 --> 39:49.286
