39:50.985 --> 39:53.366
- Amazing.
- Practice with me.

39:53.425 --> 39:55.065
- Let me try it.
- Alright.

39:55.065 --> 39:56.465
- Try it.
- Tenth ring.

39:56.465 --> 39:58.186
- Who did it?
- Really?

39:58.186 --> 40:00.966
Sheng? Sheng, was that you?

40:00.990 --> 40:03.565
Five, seven, ten.

40:04.065 --> 40:08.485
